data.title: Wild Rose Community Information
data.meta_description: RentFaster.ca is the ultimate platform to list or find rental stats in the Wild Rose community. Know more about Wild Rose community closest schools, libraries, bus routes, landmark and neighbouring communities.
data.text:
Wild Rose is a newer residential neighbourhood located in south east Edmonton, Alberta, Canada located just to the east of Mill Woods.

The neighbourhood is bounded on the east by 17 Street, on the west by 34 Street and on the north by 38 Avenue. The southern boundary with Silver Berry follows an irregular east-west line that does not correspond to any single roadway.

There is one school in the neighbourhood, Father Michael Troy Junior High School, operated by Edmonton's separate school system.
